sequenceDiagram
    actor Agronom as Agronom
    participant UI as Frontend React
    participant API as ActivityController
    participant Service as ActivityService
    participant DB as MySQL

    Agronom->>UI: Completeaza formularul lucrarii
    UI->>API: Trimite cererea de creare
    API->>Service: createActivity(dto, utilizatorCurent)

    Service->>DB: Verifica parcela, muncitorii, utilajele si materialele
    DB-->>Service: Returneaza datele necesare

    Service->>Service: Valideaza apartenenta la ferma curenta
    Service->>DB: Salveaza activitatea si relatiile asociate
    DB-->>Service: Confirma salvarea

    Service-->>API: Activitate creata
    API-->>UI: Raspuns de succes
    UI-->>Agronom: Lucrarea apare in lista activitatilor
